title: Fyre Fest Flames May Finally Be Extinguished by Recent Settlement
description:
Remember the epic 2017 Fyre Festival? Hopefully it’s not because you spent thousands to get there and ended up stranded in a Sandals parking lot...take a walk down memory lane with us and find out the latest on legal relief for the Fyre Festival attendees.
